Author: magele758 <5292001+magele758@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Tue Jul 14 10:28:04 2026 +0800

    fix(worker-host): keep own-host traffic local and preserve remote Relay bases

    Worker desktops that open on localhost while pointing at another machine's
    Remote/Relay must not rewrite those bases onto localhost, and requests for
    this machine's own host id must use /api (with server loopback) instead of
    bouncing through Relay.

